node.title: Clayton King and I talking Jesus

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Lowe in Seaside, Florida with @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 5 people, child, people standing, beach and ocean.

node.text: Our vacation has come to an end. The kids had fun and I’m positive I don’t want to see any of them for a very long time.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Sean Lowe in Seaside, Florida. May be an image of 3 people, child, people standing and beach.

node.text: We made it to Florida! Now someone get these kids so I can take a vacation.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on August 11, 2021 tagging @catherinegiudici. May be an image of 1 person, baby and outdoors.

node.text: I informed Isaiah that he will be raising the other two now because I’ve had my fill of the whole parenting thing. So far he’s proving to be a pretty good dad. Also, Mia’s hairstyle is incredible.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on August 10, 2021 tagging @pjmasks. May be an image of 2 people, child and indoor.

node.text: PJ Masks - Power Up! Our family is super excited that our favorite trio, Catboy, Owlette and Gekko, are back with a brand new, 2-part special, Ninja Power Up, launching Season 5 on Friday, August 13 at 1 pm ET/PT on Disney Junior! We got an inside scoop on what’s new this season including NEW hero powers, a NEW powered-up HQ and NEW characters like Orticia and Pirate Robot (Samuel, Isaiah, and Mia want to know - will they be friends or nighttime baddies?!) We love watching these guys, and can’t wait to catch NEW episodes every Friday at 1 pm ET/PT on Disney Junior. @pjmasks #PJMasks #PJMasksSeason5 #PJPowerUp #ad

node.text: Barely knew her when I proposed on The Bachelor and it was the best, most irresponsible decision I’ve ever made.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Sean Lowe on August 09, 2021 tagging @chameleoncoffee. May be an image of 2 people, drink, indoor and text that says 'PA CHAMELEON COLD-BREW COFFEE S'.

node.text: I’ve never been so in love. Her beauty, boldness, and flavor had me from the beginning. I love you so much @chameleoncoffee!  #BringThatCraftHome #sponsored

node.text: #PaidEggvertising Ommm… let (that’s a quality dad joke right there) me tell you about a tasty little treat I just discovered- @justcrackanegg has omelet rounds and they are so delicious! Heat them up in under a minute and enjoy a delicious breakfast treat on the go so you have more time to spend with your favorite child. Try them and thank me later! #getouttahere

node.text: Sometimes I get emotional thinking that one day Mia will be all grown up and locked in her room because her daddy is the only man she will ever love.
